\c 61
\s Dhavhidhi anovimba naMwari pakutambudzika kwake
\p Kumutungamiriri wekuimba. Nemutengeranwa. \add Pisarema\add* raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Inzwai, Mwari, kuchema kwangu, teererai kumunyengetero wangu.
\p
\v 2 Ndichadana kwamuri ndiri pamugumo wepanyika, kana moyo wangu wopera, nditungamirirei kudombo rakakwirira kundidarika.
\v 3 Nokuti manga muri utiziro hwangu, shongwe yakasimba kubva pamuvengi wangu.
\v 4 Ndichagara mutende renyu kusvika rinhi narinhi; ndichatizira kumupendero wemunyasi memapapiro enyu.
\v 5 Nokuti imwi Mwari makanzwa mhiko dzangu; maka\add ndi\add*pa nhaka nevanotya zita renyu.
\v 6 Muchawedzera mazuva pamazuva amambo; makore ake achava sezera nezera.
\v 7 Achagara pamberi paMwari nkusvika rinhi narinhi, mugadze ngoni nechokwadi, kuti zvimuchengete.
\p
\v 8 Naizvozvo ndichaimbira zita renyu rumbidzo kusvika rinhi narinhi, kuti ndizadzise mhiko dzangu zuva nezuva.
